2064377,"uid":16676,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-14T19:18:45.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.hkcnews.com/article/21519/sing_hallelujah_to_the_lord-%E5%9F%BA%E7%9D%A3%E5%BE%92-%E6%94%BF%E5%BA%9C%E7%B8%BD%E9%83%A8-21531/sing-hallelujah%E7%84%A1%E9%99%90%E5%94%B1-%E8%B7%A8%E5%AE%97%E6%B4%BE%E4%BF%A1%E5%BE%92%E8%87%AA%E7%99%BC%E6%99%9D%E5%A4%9C%E5%AE%88%E8%AD%B7%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hkcnews.com%2Farticle%2F21519%2Fsing_hallelujah_to_the_lord-%25E5%259F%25BA%25E7%259D%25A3%25E5%25BE%2592-%25E6%2594%25BF%25E5%25BA%259C%25E7%25B8%25BD%25E9%2583%25A8-21531%2Fsing-hallelujah%25E7%2584%25A1%25E9%2599%2590%25E5%2594%25B1-%25E8%25B7%25A8%25E5%25AE%2597%25E6%25B4%25BE%25E4%25BF%25A1%25E5%25BE%2592%25E8%2587%25AA%25E7%2599%25BC%25E6%2599%259D%25E5%25A4%259C%25E5%25AE%2588%25E8%25AD%25B7%25E9%25A6%2599%25E6%25B8%25AF&d=B%2FbWfq3Pg5BEfhRE9gwZ8mztmS%2FM%2FHF6fRawSWcCn68%3D&h=b4329733\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.hkcnews.com/article/21519/sing_hallelujah_to_the_lord-%E5%9F%BA%E7%9D%A3%E5%BE%92-%E6%94%BF%E5%BA%9C%E7%B8%BD%E9%83%A8-21531/sing-hallelujah%E7%84%A1%E9%99%90%E5%94%B1-%E8%B7%A8%E5%AE%97%E6%B4%BE%E4%BF%A1%E5%BE%92%E8%87%AA%E7%99%BC%E6%99%9D%E5%A4%9C%E5%AE%88%E8%AD%B7%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF</a><br />\nSing Hallelujah無限唱 跨宗派信徒自發晝夜守護香港"},{"pid":"74609d04649805c57a09c317862218c4a36c0def","tid":2064377,"uid":288370,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"2e447d90aaca3f62ecc981f3f381303fba567dae","tid":2064377,"uid":161430,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-14T19:06:43.000Z","msg":"推<br />\n重新唱返呢首啦以後"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-14T19:18:58.000Z","msg":"可以喎 好過而家啲集會咁 十分鐘唱三次《願榮光》<br />\n係有代表性 但不停 loop 好 odd <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"24897c853e703908a8aeee1874ef944f26b815e4","tid":2064377,"uid":85751,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-14T19:19:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"565689cfcfcf577cbd7fe1f234bf9155d09c4d05","tid":2064377,"uid":16676,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"da152c7f2dcf9dd6961f407d861ad96f365db1f9","tid":2064377,"uid":200135,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-14T19:00:10.000Z","msg":"自從嗰一晚之後 耶撚呢隻字就係連燈消失咗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n多謝各位嗰一晚唱咗通宵<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-14T19:19:56.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://christiantimes.org.hk/Common/Reader/News/ShowNews.jsp?Nid=162408&amp;Pid=104&amp;Version=0&amp;Cid=2052&amp;Charset=big5_hkscs\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fchristiantimes.org.hk%2FCommon%2FReader%2FNews%2FShowNews.jsp%3FNid%3D162408%26Pid%3D104%26Version%3D0%26Cid%3D2052%26Charset%3Dbig5_hkscs&d=B%2FbWfq3Pg5BEfhRE9gwZ8mztmS%2FM%2FHF6fRawSWcCn68%3D&h=ad5c63a5\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://christiantimes.org.hk/Common/Reader/News/ShowNews.jsp?Nid=162408&amp;Pid=104&amp;Version=0&amp;Cid=2052&amp;Charset=big5_hkscs</a><br />\n<ins>611晚教會我們的兩件事<br />\n政神學家 / 2020年6月12日</ins><br />\n<br />\n611當晚，整個金鐘都充滿著「山雨欲來風滿樓」的氛圍，地鐵站內有不少警員駐守，並截查途人（以年輕人為主）。同時，有一小群非常關注反送中的教牧在政總前舉辦祈禱會，為反送中運動祈禱守望。本來這只是一場平平無奇的祈禱會，但是集會完結後不少基督徒並沒有離開，反而留守現場，重複唱著祈禱會的最後一首詩歌Sing Hallelujah to the Lord，一唱就唱到翌日早上。Sing Hallelujah to the Lord從來只有同一句歌詞，聽起來枯燥無味，更別說要重複同一首詩歌一整晚了，普通人根本沒有這樣的耐力。然而，愈來愈多途人，不論他們信主與否，都受到感動一同加入唱詩的行列。基督徒在這晚的表現，使那些輕看他們的香港人大跌眼鏡。從此，社交媒體上再沒有「耶L」，取而代之的是「教徒」、「聖徒」等尊稱，天國子民與香港抗爭者正式connect。"}]}